data.description: For Sale or Trade!* Beautiful two-story home with lots of potential, includes an additional 5,227 square foot lot right next door. Total lot size of 16,117 square feet. Imagine constructing another house to accommodate extended family or generating additional rental income. Alternatively, utilize this vast space to park your recreational vehicles, boats, or any other toys. This home offers the tranquility of the surrounding open land and rolling hills. As you step inside, the interiors welcome you with an open and airy ambiance. The living and dining area are bathed in warm and neutral paint, creating an atmosphere of comfort. Transition from the living area to the kitchen, offering an abundant cabinet space and ample counters. The living quarters are designed for comfort and privacy. Spacious guest bedrooms share generously sized guest bathroom. The master suite provides a serene retreat from the world outside. The master bathroom, complete with a separate soaking tub and shower, is an oasis of relaxation, allowing you to unwind. The additional lot next door is an incredible asset, enhances the value of your investment. To explore the possibilities, it's advisable to consult the city regarding building requirements for the adjacent lot (APN #: 375-293-054).
